This repository contains third-party emulator cores in the 'src/' directory
which are compiled to WebAssembly. These cores are owned by their respective
copyright holders and are subject to their own licensing terms, including
strict NON-COMMERCIAL restrictions for SNES and Genesis/Mega Drive emulation:

1. NES Core (Agnes):
   - Location: src/nes/
   - License: MIT License (Copyright (c) 2019 Krzysztof Gabis)
   - Permissive, open-source.

2. SNES Core (Snes9x):
   - Location: src/snes9x/
   - License: Snes9x License (Copyright 1996 - 2026 Snes9x Team) + GPL v2 (ZSNES/ndssfc code)
   - Restriction: PERSONAL / NON-COMMERCIAL USE ONLY.

3. Genesis / Mega Drive Core (Genesis Plus GX):
   - Location: src/md/
   - License: Custom Non-Commercial Copyleft License (Copyright Charles MacDonald, Eke-Eke)
              + LGPL v2.1+ (Nuked OPN2, Blip Buffer, NTSC filter)
   - Restriction: STRICTLY NON-COMMERCIAL USE. Redistributing modified source code
                  requires full source disclosure of all linked components.

Please refer to the LICENSE/copyright files within each respective subdirectory
under 'src/' for their full licensing terms.

